<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EEC) NO 1224/81 OF 7 MAY 1981 RELATING TO A SPECIAL MEASURE FOLLOWING THE ALTERATION OF THE REPRESENTATIVE RATE FOR THE GERMAN MARK, IN CONNECTION WITH THE TENDER SYSTEM FOR THE SUPPLY OF MILK PRODUCTS AS FOOD AID </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 1224/81, mis k&auml;sitleb Saksa marga tasakaalustamiskursi muutmise j&auml;rgset erimeedet seoses piimatoodete toiduabina tarnimist k&auml;sitleva pakkumiss&uuml;steemiga 7. mai 1981 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> COMMUNITIES, HAVING REGARD TO THE TREATY ESTABLISHING THE EUROPEAN ECONOMIC COMMUNITY, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> HAVING REGARD TO COUNCIL REGULATION (EEC) NO 878/77 OF 26 APRIL 1977 ON THE EXCHANGE RATES TO BE APPLIED IN AGRICULTURE (1), AS LAST AMENDED BY REGULATION (EEC) NO 850/81 (2), AND IN PARTICULAR ARTICLE 5 THEREOF, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 26. aprilli 1977. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 878/77 p&otilde;llumajanduses kohaldatavate vahetuskursside kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 850/81, (2) eriti selle artiklit 5, </eesti>
<inglise> WHEREAS ARTICLE 4 OF REGULATION (EEC) NO 878/77 MADE APPLICABLE THE PROVISIONS OF COUNCIL REGULATION (EEC) NO 1134/68 OF 30 JULY 1968 FIXING THE IMPLEMENTING RULES OF REGULATION (EEC) NO 653/68 ON CONDITIONS FOR ALTERATIONS TO THE VALUE OF THE UNIT OF ACCOUNT USED FOR THE COMMON AGRICULTURAL POLICY (3); WHEREAS IN CERTAIN CASES REGULATION (EEC) NO 1134/68 STIPULATES IN CERTAIN CASES THAT ANY INDIVIDUAL WHO HAS CONCLUDED AN AGREEMENT WITH AN INTERVENTION AGENCY FOR A GIVEN OPERATION MAY, ON REQUEST, OBTAIN CANCELLATION OF HIS COMMITMENTS; WHEREAS, HOWEVER, ARTICLE 4 OF REGULATION (EEC) NO 878/77 STIPULATES THAT THE SECOND SUBPARAGRAPH OF ARTICLE 4 (1) OF REGULATION (EEC) NO 1134/68 IS TO BE APPLIED ONLY IF THE APPLICATION OF THE NEW REPRESENTATIVE RATES ENTAILS A DISADVANTAGE; WHEREAS IT ALSO STIPULATES THAT THE DISADVANTAGE CAN BE OFFSET BY AN APPROPRIATE MEASURE; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 878/77 artikli 4 alusel kohaldatakse n&otilde;ukogu 30. juuli 1968. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1134/68 (millega m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks &uuml;hise p&otilde;llumajanduspoliitika raames kasutatava arvestus&uuml;hiku v&auml;&auml;rtuse muutmise tingimusi k&auml;sitleva m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 653/68 rakenduseeskirjad) (3) s&auml;tteid; teatatavatel juhtudel n&auml;hakse m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1134/68 ette, et isik, kes on s&otilde;lminud teatava tehingu kohta sekkumisametiga kokkuleppe, v&otilde;ib taotluse korral saavutada oma kohustuste t&uuml;histamise; m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 878/77 artikliga 4 n&auml;hakse siiski ette, et m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1134/68 artikli 4 l&otilde;ike 1 teist l&otilde;iku kohaldatakse &uuml;ksnes juhul, kui uute tasakaalustamiskursside kohaldamine p&otilde;hjustab halvemuse; k&otilde;nealuse artikliga n&auml;hakse samuti ette, et halvemust saab h&uuml;vitada kohase meetme abil; </eesti>
<inglise> WHEREAS THE APPLICATION OF THESE RULES TO SUPPLIES OF FOOD AID STILL TO BE MADE UNDER COMMISSION REGULATION (EEC) NO 303/77 (4), AS LAST AMENDED BY REGULATION (EEC) NO 3474/80 (5), FOR WHICH CONTRACTS WERE AWARDED BEFORE 6 APRIL 1981, ENABLES SUCCESSFUL TENDERERS TO THE GERMAN INTERVENTION AGENCY TO OBTAIN CANCELLATION OF THEIR COMMITMENTS; WHEREAS, IN THE FIRST PLACE, LARGE-SCALE USE OF THIS FACILITY WOULD JEOPARDIZE EXECUTION OF THE COMMUNITY ' S COMMITMENTS TO THE RELEVANT FOOD-AID BENEFICIARIES; </inglise>
<eesti> k&otilde;nealuste eeskirjade kohaldamine nende toiduabi tarnete suhtes, mis komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 303/77 (4) (viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 3474/80 (5)) alusel tuleb veel sooritada ning mille kohta on s&otilde;lmitud lepingud enne 6. aprilli 1981, v&otilde;imaldab Saksamaa sekkumisametile edukate pakkumiste esitajatel saavutada oma kohustuste t&uuml;histamise; k&otilde;nealuse v&otilde;imaluse laialdane kasutamine ohustab &uuml;henduse kohustuste t&auml;itmist asjakohase toiduabi saajate ees; </eesti>
<inglise> WHEREAS, SECONDLY, THIS FACILITY DOES NOT BY ITSELF ALWAYS COVER THE SUCCESSFUL TENDERERS AGAINST ANY DISADVANTAGES SUBSISTING OR RESULTING FROM THE CANCELLATION OF THEIR COMMITMENTS TO THE COMMUNITY, NOTABLY WHERE SUCH SUCCESSFUL TENDERERS HAVE ALREADY ACCEPTED OTHER COMMITMENTS RELATING TO THE PROVISION OF THE AGREED SUPPLY; </inglise>
<eesti> lisaks sellele ei kaitse k&otilde;nealune v&otilde;imalus alati edukaid pakkujaid nende poolt &uuml;henduse suhtes v&otilde;etud kohustuste t&uuml;histamisest tuleneva mis tahes halvemuse eest, eriti kui k&otilde;nealused edukad pakkujad on juba v&otilde;tnud endale teisi kokkulepitud tarne sooritamisega seotud kohustusi; </eesti>
<inglise> WHEREAS, IN THESE CIRCUMSTANCES, THE MOST APPROPRIATE MEASURE TO AVOID ANY RISK OF DISADVANTAGE CONSISTS IN STIPULATING THAT THE AMOUNTS EXPRESSED IN GERMAN MARKS, AS ORIGINALLY AGREED BETWEEN THOSE CONCERNED AND THE GERMAN INTERVENTION AGENCY, SHOULD NOT BE AFFECTED BY THE CHANGE IN THE REPRESENTATIVE RATE FOR THE GERMAN MARK; </inglise>
<eesti> sellisel juhul on k&otilde;ige kohasem s&auml;testada halvemuse ohu v&auml;ltimise meetmena, et Saksa marga tasakaalustamiskursi muutmine ei m&otilde;juta Saksa markades v&auml;ljendatud summasid, milles asjaomased isikud ja Saksamaa sekkumisamet on algselt kokku leppinud; </eesti>
<inglise> WHEREAS THE MEASURES PROVIDED FOR IN THIS REGULATION ARE IN ACCORDANCE WITH THE OPINION OF THE MANAGEMENT COMMITTEE FOR MILK AND MILK PRODUCTS, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las piima- ja piimatooteturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> ARTICLE 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> WITHOUT PREJUDICE TO THE RIGHT OF CANCELLATION CONFERRED BY THE LAST SUBPARAGRAPH OF ARTICLE 4 (1) OF REGULATION (EEC) NO 1134/68, THE REPRESENTATIVE RATE FOR THE GERMAN MARK VALID BEFORE 6 APRIL 1981 SHALL APPLY, IF THE PERSON CONCERNED SO REQUESTS, TO FOOD-AID SUPPLIES MADE FROM THAT DATE ONWARDS PURSUANT TO REGULATION (EEC) NO 303/77 PROVIDED THE PERSON CONCERNED, NOT INVOKING THE AFORESAID RIGHT, HAS BEEN AWARDED THE RELEVANT CONTRACT BY THE GERMAN INTERVENTION AGENCY BEFORE 6 APRIL 1981. </inglise>
<eesti> Ilma et see piiraks m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1134/68 artikli 4 l&otilde;ike 1 viimase l&otilde;iguga etten&auml;htud t&uuml;histamis&otilde;iguse kohaldamist, kohaldatakse asjaomase isiku taotluse korral enne 6. aprilli 1981 kehtinud Saksa marga tasakaalustamiskurssi p&auml;rast k&otilde;nealust kuup&auml;eva m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 303/77 kohaselt sooritatud toiduabi tarnete suhtes, tingimusel et asjaomane isik on eespool nimetatud &otilde;igusele tuginemata s&otilde;lminud enne 6. aprilli 1981 Saksamaa sekkumisametiga asjakohase lepingu. </eesti>
<inglise> ARTICLE 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> THIS REGULATION SHALL ENTER INTO FORCE ON THE DAY OF ITS PUBLICATION IN THE OFFICIAL JOURNAL OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub selle Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas avaldamise p&auml;eval. K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> THIS REGULATION SHALL BE BINDING IN ITS ENTIRETY AND DIRECTLY APPLICABLE IN ALL MEMBER STATES. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 7. mai 1981 Komisjoni nimel komisjoni liige POUL DALSAGER </eesti>
